toFilterItems

public static final SearchFilterItems toFilterItems(java.lang.String searchString,
                                                    java.util.List<SearchCategory> searchCats,
                                                    java.util.List<SearchCategory> allCats)
Factory method to generate common SearchFilterItems. Note that the more exotic search filter item values (tags, last update dates) are set by the search itself, as it contains information on this.

Parameters:
searchString - search String entered by the user.
searchCats - categories being searched, a subset of allCats.
allCats - all categories allowed to search on.
Returns:
SearchFilterItems corresponding to these filters.
